      "text": "<div class=\"created-with-ak-editor content-wrapper\"><p>The label on the device must be changed or reprinted, and a new label with the name 'LEL-VAC-VPCONxx' must be attached. The device appears to be for temporary use. Also the relevant cabling <a href=\"https://servicedesk.infn.it/secure/ShowObject.jspa?id=138466\">VPCON18-ser</a> has to be changed to VPCONxx-ser</p><p></p></div>",
